      "Streaks, resets, and difficulty weighting drive the table.": "Awọn ṣiṣan, awọn atunto, ati iṣoro iwuwo wakọ tabili naa.",
      "Strong form, locked-in minutes, and positive sentiment usually push the estimate upward.": "Fọọmu ti o lagbara, titiipa-ni iṣẹju, ati itara ti o dara nigbagbogbo Titari iṣiro naa si oke.",
