      "Tactical debate, set-piece tracking, and momentum swings are driving the room.": "Jomitoro ọgbọn, ipasẹ-nkan ti a ṣeto, ati awọn swings iyara n wa yara naa.",
      "Tactical storyline": "Imo itan itan",
      "Target profile match": "Ifojusi profaili baramu",
      "Team of the Week": "Egbe Osu",
      "The better version of this page links role changes, watchlist alerts, and youth radar into one scouting rhythm so the eye never falls into dead space.": "Ẹya ti o dara julọ ti oju-iwe yii ṣe ọna asopọ awọn iyipada ipa, awọn titaniji atokọ, ati radar ọdọ sinu ohun orin iwo kan ki oju ko ṣubu sinu aaye ti o ku.",
      "The biggest late-season movement still comes from U21 players whose role value grows faster than raw goal volume.": "Iyika akoko-pẹ ti o tobi julọ tun wa lati ọdọ awọn oṣere U21 ti iye ipa wọn dagba yiyara ju iwọn ibi-aise aise lọ.",
      "The current dashboard story is less about raw goal output and more about where his first touches are landing. When Madrid lock him closer to the box, Vinicius gets a cleaner second wave and Kroos can play earlier through the inside lane.": "Itan dasibodu lọwọlọwọ kere si nipa iṣelọpọ ibi-aise aise ati diẹ sii nipa ibi ti awọn ifọwọkan akọkọ rẹ ti n balẹ. Nigbati Madrid tii i sunmọ apoti, Vinicius gba igbi keji ti o mọ ati Kroos le ṣere ni iṣaaju nipasẹ ọna inu.",
      "The current planner treats women’s recruitment watch items with the same visual seriousness as the men’s pathway instead of tucking them into a side mode.": "Oluṣeto lọwọlọwọ ṣe itọju awọn ohun wiwo rikurumenti obinrin pẹlu pataki wiwo kanna bi ọna awọn ọkunrin dipo fifi wọn sinu ipo ẹgbẹ kan.",
      "The current prototype feed keeps surfacing teams that can stay calm after losing field tilt, and Inter keep rating highly there.": "Awọn kikọ sii Afọwọkọ lọwọlọwọ ntọju awọn ẹgbẹ ti o wa ni iwaju ti o le dakẹ lẹhin sisọnu aaye, ati Inter tẹsiwaju ni idiyele giga nibẹ.",
      "The current wage floor is inflating squad-balance risk more than fee risk.": "Ilẹ-ilẹ oya lọwọlọwọ n fa eewu iwọntunwọnsi ẹgbẹ diẹ sii ju eewu ọya lọ.",
      "The explorer is still running on mock player data, but the visible filters now work for real. Try broadening a range or hit reset to reopen the full demo database.": "Oluwadi naa tun nṣiṣẹ lori data ẹrọ orin ẹlẹgàn, ṣugbọn awọn asẹ ti o han ni bayi ṣiṣẹ fun gidi. Gbìyànjú láti gbilẹ̀ síbi kan tàbí kíkọlu àtúntò láti tún ibùdó data demo ni kikun sii.",
      "The fixture stack now makes load planning part of the tactical picture rather than just a medical note.": "Iṣakojọpọ imuduro bayi jẹ ki igbero fifuye jẹ apakan ti aworan ọgbọn kuku ju akọsilẹ iṣoogun kan lọ.",
      "The following feed should feel alive, varied, and still honest": "Ifunni atẹle yẹ ki o ni rilara laaye, yatọ, ati tun jẹ ooto",
      "The lower transfer desk should still feel like part of the same active room": "Iduro gbigbe isalẹ yẹ ki o tun lero bi apakan ti yara ti nṣiṣe lọwọ kanna",
      "The page is now a competition hub, not just four floating tables.": "Oju-iwe naa jẹ ibudo idije bayi, kii ṣe awọn tabili lilefoofo mẹrin nikan.",
      "The page now carries enough supporting panels to feel like a real transfer desk instead of one floating hero module.": "Oju-iwe naa ni bayi gbe awọn panẹli atilẹyin to lati rilara bi tabili gbigbe gidi dipo module akọni lilefoofo kan.",
      "The page now feels like a real part of the football product instead of two floating cards in a dark void.": "Oju-iwe naa ni rilara bi apakan gidi ti ọja bọọlu dipo awọn kaadi lilefoofo meji ni ofo dudu.",
      "The page now uses football-native room types, not generic social placeholders.": "Oju-iwe naa nlo awọn oriṣi yara abinibi-bọọlu, kii ṣe awọn aye ti awujọ jeneriki.",
      "The Palmeiras holding midfielder keeps showing first-contact calm under pressure. His interceptions are impressive, but the bigger point is how often he stabilizes the next pass.": "Aarin aarin Palmeiras n tọju ifọkanbalẹ olubasọrọ akọkọ labẹ titẹ. Awọn idawọle rẹ jẹ iwunilori, ṣugbọn aaye ti o tobi julọ ni iye igba ti o ṣe iduroṣinṣin iwe-iwọle atẹle.",
      "The point is to show structure, intent, and future football logic without pretending the backend systems already exist.": "Ojuami ni lati ṣafihan eto, idi, ati ọgbọn bọọlu iwaju lai ṣe dibọn awọn eto ẹhin ti wa tẹlẹ.",
      "The right rail should add football meaning, not just stack more text cards": "Iṣinipopada ọtun yẹ ki o ṣafikun itumọ bọọlu, kii ṣe akopọ awọn kaadi ọrọ diẹ sii",
      "The same product logic applies here: big women’s fixtures belong in the same room ecology.": "Ọja kannaa kannaa kan nibi: awọn imuduro ti awọn obinrin ti o tobi jẹ ninu ilolupo yara kanna.",
      "Their last four matches show a sharper overlap-to-cutback pattern and better counterpress recovery.": "Awọn ere-kere mẹrin ti o kẹhin wọn ṣe afihan ilana fifin-si-cutback ti o nipọn ati imularada counterpress ti o dara julọ.",
      "Their last three defensive structures collapse passing lanes faster, which is changing the Bellingham load in possession.": "Awọn ẹya igbeja mẹta ti o kẹhin wọn ṣubu awọn ọna gbigbe ni iyara, eyiti o n yi ẹru Bellingham pada ni ohun-ini.",
      "Their latest run of matches keeps reinforcing the same wide-to-box pattern, and it belongs in the main feed, not a separate lane.": "Ṣiṣe awọn ere-kere tuntun wọn ntọju imudara ilana iwọn-si-apoti kanna, ati pe o jẹ ninu kikọ sii akọkọ, kii ṣe ọna ti o yatọ.",
      "Their right-half-space creation keeps widening the shot map.": "Iṣẹda aaye-idaji-ọtun wọn ntọju maapu ibọn naa gbooro.",
      "Themes": "Awọn akori",
