      "Team of the Week": "本周最佳团队",
      "The better version of this page links role changes, watchlist alerts, and youth radar into one scouting rhythm so the eye never falls into dead space.": "此页面的更好版本将角色变化、观察列表警报和青年雷达链接到一个侦察节奏中，这样眼睛就不会陷入死角。",
      "The biggest late-season movement still comes from U21 players whose role value grows faster than raw goal volume.": "赛季末最大的变动仍然来自 U21 球员，他们的角色价值增长速度快于原始进球数。",
      "The current dashboard story is less about raw goal output and more about where his first touches are landing. When Madrid lock him closer to the box, Vinicius gets a cleaner second wave and Kroos can play earlier through the inside lane.": "当前的仪表板故事较少关注原始目标输出，而更多关注他的第一次触球落地的位置。当皇马将他锁在禁区附近时，维尼修斯会获得更干净的第二波进攻，而克罗斯则可以更早地从内线进攻。",
      "The current planner treats women’s recruitment watch items with the same visual seriousness as the men’s pathway instead of tucking them into a side mode.": "当前的规划者以与男性途径相同的视觉严肃性对待女性招募观察项目，而不是将其塞入侧面模式。",
      "The current prototype feed keeps surfacing teams that can stay calm after losing field tilt, and Inter keep rating highly there.": "当前的原型反馈让球队在失去球场倾斜后能够保持冷静，国际米兰也保持了很高的评价。",
      "The current wage floor is inflating squad-balance risk more than fee risk.": "目前的工资下限对球队平衡风险的影响大于费用风险。",
      "The explorer is still running on mock player data, but the visible filters now work for real. Try broadening a range or hit reset to reopen the full demo database.": "浏览器仍在模拟玩家数据上运行，但可见过滤器现在可以正常工作。尝试扩大范围或点击重置以重新打开完整的演示数据库。",
      "The fixture stack now makes load planning part of the tactical picture rather than just a medical note.": "现在，夹具堆栈使负载计划成为战术图的一部分，而不仅仅是医疗记录。",
      "The following feed should feel alive, varied, and still honest": "以下提要应该让人感觉充满活力、多样化且仍然诚实",
      "The lower transfer desk should still feel like part of the same active room": "较低的转乘台仍应感觉像是同一个活动房间的一部分",
      "The page is now a competition hub, not just four floating tables.": "该页面现在是一个竞赛中心，而不仅仅是四个浮动桌子。",
      "The page now carries enough supporting panels to feel like a real transfer desk instead of one floating hero module.": "该页面现在带有足够的支撑面板，感觉就像一个真正的转接台，而不是一个浮动的英雄模块。",
      "The page now feels like a real part of the football product instead of two floating cards in a dark void.": "现在，该页面感觉就像是足球产品的真实部分，而不是黑暗空间中的两张浮动卡片。",
      "The page now uses football-native room types, not generic social placeholders.": "该页面现在使用足球原生房间类型，而不是通用的社交占位符。",
      "The Palmeiras holding midfielder keeps showing first-contact calm under pressure. His interceptions are impressive, but the bigger point is how often he stabilizes the next pass.": "帕尔梅拉斯的控球中场在压力下始终表现出第一次接触时的冷静。他的拦截令人印象深刻，但更重要的是他稳定下一次传球的频率。",
      "The point is to show structure, intent, and future football logic without pretending the backend systems already exist.": "重点是展示结构、意图和未来的足球逻辑，而不假装后端系统已经存在。",
      "The right rail should add football meaning, not just stack more text cards": "正确的栏杆应该增加足球的意义，而不仅仅是堆叠更多的文字卡",
      "The same product logic applies here: big women’s fixtures belong in the same room ecology.": "同样的产品逻辑也适用于此：大型女性灯具属于同一个房间生态。",
      "Their last four matches show a sharper overlap-to-cutback pattern and better counterpress recovery.": "他们的最后四场比赛显示出更尖锐的重叠回撤模式和更好的反压迫恢复。",
      "Their last three defensive structures collapse passing lanes faster, which is changing the Bellingham load in possession.": "他们的最后三个防守结构更快地崩溃了传球路线，这正在改变贝灵厄姆的控球负荷。",
      "Their latest run of matches keeps reinforcing the same wide-to-box pattern, and it belongs in the main feed, not a separate lane.": "他们最近的一系列比赛不断强化相同的宽禁区模式，并且它属于主饲料，而不是单独的车道。",
      "Their right-half-space creation keeps widening the shot map.": "他们的右前场空间不断扩大射门范围。",
      "Themes": "主题",
      "These preview pages now sit inside the same football product language as Market XI, instead of looking like giant heroes with nothing underneath.": "这些预览页面现在采用与 Market XI 相同的足球产品语言，而不是看起来像下面什么都没有的巨型英雄。",
      "These rooms are structured demo surfaces only. No live moderation, messaging, or presence engine is being claimed here yet.": "这些房间只是结构化演示表面。此处尚未声明实时审核、消息传递或状态引擎。",
      "They are sustaining width without exposing the first counter line, which keeps their risers stable.": "他们在不暴露第一条反击线的情况下保持宽度，这使他们的立带保持稳定。",
      "This community surface is a structured demo only, not a live messaging stack.": "该社区界面只是一个结构化演示，而不是实时消息传递堆栈。",
      "This page is denser and stronger, but still clearly marked as a concept surface.": "该页面更密集、更强大，但仍然清楚地标记为概念表面。",
