      "The better version of this page links role changes, watchlist alerts, and youth radar into one scouting rhythm so the eye never falls into dead space.": "Ụdị ibe a ka mma na-ejikọta mgbanwe ọrụ, ọkwa nlele, na radar ndị ntorobịa n'ime otu egwu egwu ka anya ghara ịdaba n'ime oghere nwụrụ anwụ.",
      "The biggest late-season movement still comes from U21 players whose role value grows faster than raw goal volume.": "Nnukwu mmegharị oge ikpeazụ ka na-abịa site n'aka ndị egwuregwu U21 nke uru ọrụ ha na-eto ngwa ngwa karịa olu ebumnuche raw.",
      "The current dashboard story is less about raw goal output and more about where his first touches are landing. When Madrid lock him closer to the box, Vinicius gets a cleaner second wave and Kroos can play earlier through the inside lane.": "Akụkọ dashboard dị ugbu a pere mpe maka mmepụta ihe mgbaru ọsọ na-enweghị isi yana ihe gbasara ebe mmetụ mbụ ya na-agbada. Mgbe Madrid kpochiri ya nso na igbe ahụ, Vinicius na-enweta ebili mmiri nke abụọ dị ọcha ma Kroos nwere ike igwu egwu na mbụ site na ụzọ ime.",
      "The current planner treats women’s recruitment watch items with the same visual seriousness as the men’s pathway instead of tucking them into a side mode.": "Onye na-eme atụmatụ ugbu a na-emeso ihe nlele mbanye ụmụ nwanyị n'otu ihe anya dị ka ụzọ ụmụ nwoke kama itinye ha na ọnọdụ akụkụ.",
      "The current prototype feed keeps surfacing teams that can stay calm after losing field tilt, and Inter keep rating highly there.": "Nri ihe ngosi dị ugbu a na-eme ka ndị otu na-agba ọsọ nwere ike nọrọ jụụ ma ọ bụrụ na ha tufuru n'ọhịa, Inter na-agakwa n'ihu ebe ahụ.",
      "The current wage floor is inflating squad-balance risk more than fee risk.": "Ala ụgwọ ọnwa dị ugbu a na-ebuli ihe egwu nguzozi squad karịa ihe egwu ego.",
      "The explorer is still running on mock player data, but the visible filters now work for real. Try broadening a range or hit reset to reopen the full demo database.": "Onye nyocha ahụ ka na-agba ọsọ na data ọkpụkpọ egwu, mana ihe nzacha a na-ahụ anya na-arụ ọrụ ugbu a n'ezie. Gbalịa ịgbasa nsoro ma ọ bụ kụọ nrụpụta ka imepee nchekwa data ngosi zuru ezu.",
      "The fixture stack now makes load planning part of the tactical picture rather than just a medical note.": "Ngwunye ihe nrụnye ugbu a na-eme atụmatụ ibu ibu akụkụ nke eserese a ma ama karịa naanị akwụkwọ ndetu ahụike.",
      "The following feed should feel alive, varied, and still honest": "Nri na-esote kwesịrị ịdị ndụ, dị iche iche, ma ka na-akwụwa aka ọtọ",
