      "The Palmeiras holding midfielder keeps showing first-contact calm under pressure. His interceptions are impressive, but the bigger point is how often he stabilizes the next pass.": "Onye egwuregwu Palmeiras na-ejide onye ọkpọ egwuregwu na-egosipụta udo kọntaktị mbụ n'okpuru nrụgide. Ntinye aka ya na-adọrọ mmasị, mana isi ihe bụ ugboro ole ọ na-eme ka ngafe na-esote guzosie ike.",
