      "Team of the Week": "Timu bora ya Wiki",
      "The better version of this page links role changes, watchlist alerts, and youth radar into one scouting rhythm so the eye never falls into dead space.": "Toleo bora la ukurasa huu huunganisha mabadiliko ya majukumu, arifa za orodha ya kutazama, na rada ya vijana kuwa mdundo mmoja wa skauti ili jicho lisianguke katika nafasi isiyofaa.",
      "The biggest late-season movement still comes from U21 players whose role value grows faster than raw goal volume.": "Harakati kubwa zaidi za mwishoni mwa msimu bado zinatokana na wachezaji wa U21 ambao thamani yao inakua haraka kuliko kiwango cha mabao ghafi.",
      "The current dashboard story is less about raw goal output and more about where his first touches are landing. When Madrid lock him closer to the box, Vinicius gets a cleaner second wave and Kroos can play earlier through the inside lane.": "Hadithi ya sasa ya dashibodi haihusu matokeo ghafi ya lengo na zaidi kuhusu mahali ambapo miguso yake ya kwanza inafika. Wakati Madrid inapomfunga karibu na eneo la goli, Vinicius anapata wimbi safi la pili na Kroos anaweza kucheza mapema kupitia mstari wa ndani.",
      "The current planner treats women’s recruitment watch items with the same visual seriousness as the men’s pathway instead of tucking them into a side mode.": "Mpangaji wa sasa hushughulikia vipengee vya saa za kuajiri wanawake kwa umakini sawa na njia ya wanaume badala ya kuviweka katika hali ya kando.",
      "The current prototype feed keeps surfacing teams that can stay calm after losing field tilt, and Inter keep rating highly there.": "Milisho ya sasa ya mfano huweka timu zinazoingia ambazo zinaweza kukaa tulivu baada ya kushindwa kuinamisha uwanja, na Inter inaendelea kukadiria hapo juu.",
      "The current wage floor is inflating squad-balance risk more than fee risk.": "Kiwango cha sasa cha mshahara kinaongeza hatari ya usawa wa kikosi zaidi ya hatari ya ada.",
      "The explorer is still running on mock player data, but the visible filters now work for real. Try broadening a range or hit reset to reopen the full demo database.": "Kichunguzi bado kinatumia data ya kicheza dhihaka, lakini vichujio vinavyoonekana sasa vinafanya kazi kweli. Jaribu kupanua masafa au gonga weka upya ili kufungua tena hifadhidata kamili ya onyesho.",
      "The fixture stack now makes load planning part of the tactical picture rather than just a medical note.": "Ratiba sasa inafanya upangaji wa mzigo kuwa sehemu ya picha ya kimbinu badala ya dokezo la matibabu tu.",
      "The following feed should feel alive, varied, and still honest": "Mlisho ufuatao unapaswa kuhisi hai, tofauti, na bado waaminifu",
      "The lower transfer desk should still feel like part of the same active room": "Dawati la chini la uhamishaji bado linapaswa kuhisi kama sehemu ya chumba kimoja kinachotumika",
      "The page is now a competition hub, not just four floating tables.": "Ukurasa huu sasa ni kitovu cha mashindano, sio meza nne tu zinazoelea.",
      "The page now carries enough supporting panels to feel like a real transfer desk instead of one floating hero module.": "Ukurasa sasa umebeba vidirisha vya kutosha vya kusaidia kuhisi kama dawati halisi la uhamishaji badala ya moduli moja ya shujaa inayoelea.",
      "The page now feels like a real part of the football product instead of two floating cards in a dark void.": "Ukurasa sasa unahisi kama sehemu halisi ya bidhaa ya mpira wa miguu badala ya kadi mbili zinazoelea kwenye utupu wa giza.",
      "The page now uses football-native room types, not generic social placeholders.": "Ukurasa huu sasa unatumia aina za vyumba vya asili vya kandanda, sio vishikilia nafasi vya kijamii.",
      "The Palmeiras holding midfielder keeps showing first-contact calm under pressure. His interceptions are impressive, but the bigger point is how often he stabilizes the next pass.": "Kiungo wa Palmeiras anayeshikilia anaendelea kuonyesha mawasiliano ya kwanza akiwa mtulivu chini ya shinikizo. Kuingilia kwake kunavutia, lakini jambo kubwa zaidi ni mara ngapi anaimarisha pasi inayofuata.",
      "The point is to show structure, intent, and future football logic without pretending the backend systems already exist.": "Hoja ni kuonyesha muundo, dhamira, na mantiki ya baadaye ya soka bila kujifanya mifumo ya nyuma tayari ipo.",
      "The right rail should add football meaning, not just stack more text cards": "Reli inayofaa inapaswa kuongeza maana ya mpira wa miguu, sio tu kuweka kadi nyingi za maandishi",
      "The same product logic applies here: big women’s fixtures belong in the same room ecology.": "Mantiki sawa ya bidhaa inatumika hapa: Ratiba kubwa za wanawake ziko katika ikolojia ya chumba kimoja.",
      "Their last four matches show a sharper overlap-to-cutback pattern and better counterpress recovery.": "Mechi zao nne za mwisho zinaonyesha muundo mkali zaidi wa kuingiliana-kwa-kukata na uokoaji bora wa kukabiliana.",
      "Their last three defensive structures collapse passing lanes faster, which is changing the Bellingham load in possession.": "Miundo yao mitatu ya mwisho ya ulinzi huporomoka njia zinazopita kwa kasi zaidi, jambo ambalo linabadilisha mzigo wa Bellingham wanaomiliki.",
      "Their latest run of matches keeps reinforcing the same wide-to-box pattern, and it belongs in the main feed, not a separate lane.": "Uendeshaji wao wa hivi punde wa mechi unaendelea kuimarisha mchoro ule ule wa upana hadi kisanduku, na ni wa mlisho mkuu, si njia tofauti.",
      "Their right-half-space creation keeps widening the shot map.": "Uundaji wao wa nafasi ya nusu ya kulia unaendelea kupanua ramani ya picha.",
      "Themes": "Mandhari",
      "These preview pages now sit inside the same football product language as Market XI, instead of looking like giant heroes with nothing underneath.": "Kurasa hizi za onyesho la kukagua sasa ziko ndani ya lugha sawa ya bidhaa za kandanda kama Market XI, badala ya kuonekana kama mashujaa wakubwa bila kitu chini.",
      "These rooms are structured demo surfaces only. No live moderation, messaging, or presence engine is being claimed here yet.": "Vyumba hivi ni nyuso za onyesho zilizoundwa tu. Bado hakuna udhibiti wa moja kwa moja, utumaji ujumbe, au injini ya uwepo inayodaiwa hapa.",
      "They are sustaining width without exposing the first counter line, which keeps their risers stable.": "Zinaendeleza upana bila kufichua safu ya kwanza ya kaunta, ambayo huweka viinua vyao kuwa thabiti.",
      "This community surface is a structured demo only, not a live messaging stack.": "Uso huu wa jumuiya ni onyesho lililoundwa pekee, si rundo la ujumbe wa moja kwa moja.",
      "This page is denser and stronger, but still clearly marked as a concept surface.": "Ukurasa huu ni mnene na una nguvu zaidi, lakini bado una alama ya wazi kama uso wa dhana.",
