      "Strong form, locked-in minutes, and positive sentiment usually push the estimate upward.": "Ifomu eliqinile, amaminithi akhiyelwe ngaphakathi, kanye nomuzwa oqondile ngokuvamile kuphakamisa ukulinganisa phezulu.",
