      "Tactical debate, set-piece tracking, and momentum swings are driving the room.": "Inkulumompikiswano yamaqhinga, ukulandelela isiqephu, nokushintshashintsha komfutho kushayela igumbi.",
      "Tactical storyline": "Indaba ehlakaniphile",
      "Target profile match": "Iphrofayela eqondisiwe efanayo",
      "Team of the Week": "Ithimba Leviki",
      "The better version of this page links role changes, watchlist alerts, and youth radar into one scouting rhythm so the eye never falls into dead space.": "Inguqulo engcono yaleli khasi ixhumanisa izinguquko zendima, izexwayiso zohlu lokubuka, ne-radar yentsha ibe isigqi esisodwa sokuhlola ukuze iso lingalokothi liwele endaweni efile.",
      "The biggest late-season movement still comes from U21 players whose role value grows faster than raw goal volume.": "Umnyakazo omkhulu wesizini edlule usavela kubadlali be-U21 inani labo lendima elikhula ngokushesha kunevolumu yegoli eluhlaza.",
      "The current dashboard story is less about raw goal output and more about where his first touches are landing. When Madrid lock him closer to the box, Vinicius gets a cleaner second wave and Kroos can play earlier through the inside lane.": "Indaba yamanje yedeshibhodi incane mayelana nokuphuma kwegoli okungavuthiwe futhi imayelana nokuthi ukuthinta kwakhe kokuqala kufika kuphi. Lapho iMadrid imvalela eduze kwebhokisi, uVinicius uthola igagasi lesibili elihlanzekile futhi uKroos angadlala ngaphambili ngomzila ongaphakathi.",
      "The current planner treats women’s recruitment watch items with the same visual seriousness as the men’s pathway instead of tucking them into a side mode.": "Umhleli wamanje uphatha izinto zewashi lokuqashwa kwabesifazane ngendlela ebucayi efana nendlela yamadoda esikhundleni sokuzishutheka kumodi eseceleni.",
      "The current prototype feed keeps surfacing teams that can stay calm after losing field tilt, and Inter keep rating highly there.": "Iprototype feed yamanje igcina amaqembu avelayo akwazi ukuhlala ezolile ngemva kokulahlekelwa ukutsheka kwenkundla, futhi i-Inter ilokhu ilinganisela phezulu lapho.",
      "The current wage floor is inflating squad-balance risk more than fee risk.": "Iholo lamanje linyusa ingozi yebhalansi yeqembu ngaphezu kwengcuphe yenkokhelo.",
      "The explorer is still running on mock player data, but the visible filters now work for real. Try broadening a range or hit reset to reopen the full demo database.": "Umhloli usasebenzisa idatha yesidlali mbumbulu, kodwa izihlungi ezibonakalayo manje zisebenza ngokwangempela. Zama ukunweba ububanzi noma shaya ukusetha kabusha ukuze uvule kabusha isizindalwazi esigcwele sedemo.",
      "The fixture stack now makes load planning part of the tactical picture rather than just a medical note.": "Isitaki sendawo manje senza ukuhlela umthwalo kube yingxenye yesithombe esihlakaniphile kunokuba kube inothi lezokwelapha.",
      "The following feed should feel alive, varied, and still honest": "Okuphakelayo okulandelayo kufanele kuzizwe kuyaphila, kuhlukahlukene, futhi kusathembekile",
      "The lower transfer desk should still feel like part of the same active room": "Ideski lokudlulisa eliphansi kusafanele lizizwe njengengxenye yegumbi elisebenzayo elifanayo",
      "The page is now a competition hub, not just four floating tables.": "Leli khasi manje seliyisikhungo sokuncintisana, hhayi nje amatafula amane antantayo.",
      "The page now carries enough supporting panels to feel like a real transfer desk instead of one floating hero module.": "Ikhasi manje liphethe amaphaneli asekelayo anele ukuze lizizwe njengedeski langempela lokudlulisa esikhundleni semojula eyodwa yeqhawe elintantayo.",
      "The page now feels like a real part of the football product instead of two floating cards in a dark void.": "Ikhasi manje selizwakala njengengxenye yangempela yomkhiqizo webhola esikhundleni samakhadi amabili antantayo esikhaleni esimnyama.",
      "The page now uses football-native room types, not generic social placeholders.": "Manje leli khasi lisebenzisa izinhlobo zamagumbi omdabu webhola lezinyawo, hhayi izibambi zendawo zomphakathi.",
      "The Palmeiras holding midfielder keeps showing first-contact calm under pressure. His interceptions are impressive, but the bigger point is how often he stabilizes the next pass.": "Umdlali wasesiswini ophethe iPalmeiras ulokhu ekhombisa ukuthintana naye okokuqala ezolile ngaphansi kwengcindezi. Ukulinganisa kwakhe kuyamangaza, kodwa iphuzu elikhulu ukuthi ulimisa kangaki iphasi elilandelayo.",
      "The point is to show structure, intent, and future football logic without pretending the backend systems already exist.": "Iphuzu liwukukhombisa ukwakheka, inhloso, kanye nomqondo webhola lezinyawo wesikhathi esizayo ngaphandle kokwenza sengathi izinhlelo ezingemuva sezivele zikhona.",
      "The right rail should add football meaning, not just stack more text cards": "Ujantshi ofanele kufanele wengeze incazelo yebhola, hhayi nje ukunqwabelanisa amakhadi ombhalo engeziwe",
      "The same product logic applies here: big women’s fixtures belong in the same room ecology.": "Umqondo ofanayo womkhiqizo uyasebenza lapha: izakhiwo ezinkulu zabesifazane zisendaweni yemvelo yegumbi elifanayo.",
      "Their last four matches show a sharper overlap-to-cutback pattern and better counterpress recovery.": "Imidlalo yabo emine yokugcina ikhombisa iphethini ecijile yokugqagqana-to-cutback kanye nokutholwa okungcono kwe-counterpress.",
      "Their last three defensive structures collapse passing lanes faster, which is changing the Bellingham load in possession.": "Izakhiwo zabo zokuzivikela ezintathu zokugcina zibhidlika imizila edlulayo ngokushesha, okushintsha umthwalo weBellingham esiwuphethe.",
      "Their latest run of matches keeps reinforcing the same wide-to-box pattern, and it belongs in the main feed, not a separate lane.": "Umdlalo wabo wakamuva wamameshi uqhubeka uqinisa iphethini efanayo yobubanzi kuya ebhokisini, futhi ingeyesiphakeli esiyinhloko, hhayi umzila ohlukile.",
      "Their right-half-space creation keeps widening the shot map.": "Ukudalwa kwabo kwesikhala esiyingxenye yesokudla kuqhubeka nokunweba imephu yokushutha.",
      "Themes": "Izindikimba",
      "These preview pages now sit inside the same football product language as Market XI, instead of looking like giant heroes with nothing underneath.": "Lawa makhasi okubuka kuqala manje ahlala ngaphakathi kolimi lomkhiqizo webhola lezinyawo ofanayo nowe-Market XI, esikhundleni sokubukeka njengamaqhawe amakhulu angenalutho ngaphansi.",
      "These rooms are structured demo surfaces only. No live moderation, messaging, or presence engine is being claimed here yet.": "Lawa magumbi ayizindawo zedemo ezakhiwe kuphela. Akukho ukulinganiswa okubukhoma, imilayezo, noma injini yobukhona efunwa lapha okwamanje.",
      "They are sustaining width without exposing the first counter line, which keeps their risers stable.": "Zibamba ububanzi ngaphandle kokuveza umugqa wokuqala wokubala, ogcina izikhuphukeli zazo zizinzile.",
      "This community surface is a structured demo only, not a live messaging stack.": "Le ndawo yomphakathi iyidemo ehlelekile kuphela, hhayi isitaki semilayezo ebukhoma.",
      "This page is denser and stronger, but still clearly marked as a concept surface.": "Leli khasi liminyene futhi liqinile, kodwa lisamakwe ngokucacile njengendawo yomqondo.",
      "This page is intentionally fuller than a placeholder, but it still does not claim live game systems, real persistence, or backend-backed competition logic.": "Leli khasi ligcwele ngamabomu kunesimeli, kodwa namanje alifuni amasistimu egeyimu ebukhoma, ukuphikelela kwangempela, noma ukuqondana kokuncintisana okusekelwe emuva.",
      "Three clubs still project inside one title window.": "Amakilabhu amathathu asasebenza ngaphakathi kwewindi lesicoco esisodwa.",
      "Three women’s names in active watch": "Amagama amathathu abesifazane ewashini elisebenzayo",
      "Title races tracked": "Izinhlanga zezihloko ziyalandelelwa",
      "Title-pressure watch in the same slate.": "Iwashi lokucindezela kwesihloko kusilayidi esifanayo.",
      "Today’s slate": "Isileti sanamuhla",
