      "Tactical debate room": "Dakin muhawara",
      "Tactical debate, set-piece tracking, and momentum swings are driving the room.": "Muhawarar dabara, saiti-yanki, da sauye-sauyen yanayi suna jan dakin.",
      "Tactical storyline": "Labari na dabara",
      "Target profile match": "Daidaita bayanin martaba",
      "Team of the Week": "Tawagar mako",
      "The better version of this page links role changes, watchlist alerts, and youth radar into one scouting rhythm so the eye never falls into dead space.": "Mafi kyawun sigar wannan shafin yana haɗa sauye-sauyen matsayi, faɗakarwar jerin sa ido, da radar matasa zuwa cikin waƙoƙi guda ɗaya don haka ido bai taɓa faɗuwa cikin mataccen sarari ba.",
      "The biggest late-season movement still comes from U21 players whose role value grows faster than raw goal volume.": "Babban motsi na ƙarshen kakar har yanzu yana fitowa daga 'yan wasan U21 waɗanda darajar rawarsu ke girma da sauri fiye da ƙarar burin burin.",
      "The current dashboard story is less about raw goal output and more about where his first touches are landing. When Madrid lock him closer to the box, Vinicius gets a cleaner second wave and Kroos can play earlier through the inside lane.": "Labarin dashboard ɗin na yanzu bai fi ƙarancin fitowar maƙasudin manufa ba da ƙari game da inda taɓawar sa ta farko ke sauka. Lokacin da Madrid ta kulle shi kusa da akwatin, Vinicius ya sami tsaftataccen igiyar ruwa ta biyu kuma Kroos na iya taka leda a baya ta hanyar ciki.",
      "The current planner treats women’s recruitment watch items with the same visual seriousness as the men’s pathway instead of tucking them into a side mode.": "Mai tsarawa na yanzu yana kula da kayan kallon daukar aikin mata tare da mahimmancin gani iri ɗaya da hanyar maza maimakon sanya su cikin yanayin gefe.",
      "The current prototype feed keeps surfacing teams that can stay calm after losing field tilt, and Inter keep rating highly there.": "Abincin samfurin na yanzu yana kiyaye ƙungiyoyi masu tasowa waɗanda za su iya natsuwa bayan sun yi rashin karkata filin, kuma Inter ta ci gaba da ƙima sosai a can.",
      "The current wage floor is inflating squad-balance risk more than fee risk.": "Tsarin albashi na yanzu yana haɓaka haɗarin ma'auni na ƙungiyar fiye da haɗarin kuɗi.",
      "The explorer is still running on mock player data, but the visible filters now work for real. Try broadening a range or hit reset to reopen the full demo database.": "Har yanzu mai binciken yana gudana akan bayanan ɗan wasa na izgili, amma abubuwan tacewa da ake gani yanzu suna aiki da gaske. Gwada faɗaɗa kewayo ko buga sake saiti don sake buɗe cikakken bayanan demo.",
      "The fixture stack now makes load planning part of the tactical picture rather than just a medical note.": "Tarin madaidaicin yanzu yana sanya shirin ɗaukar kaya wani ɓangare na hoton dabara maimakon bayanin likita kawai.",
      "The following feed should feel alive, varied, and still honest": "Abincin da ke gaba ya kamata ya ji da rai, bambanta, kuma har yanzu gaskiya",
      "The lower transfer desk should still feel like part of the same active room": "Teburin canja wuri na ƙasa ya kamata ya kasance yana jin kamar sashe na ɗaki ɗaya mai aiki",
      "The page is now a competition hub, not just four floating tables.": "Shafin yanzu ya zama cibiyar gasa, ba kawai teburi masu iyo guda hudu ba.",
      "The page now carries enough supporting panels to feel like a real transfer desk instead of one floating hero module.": "Shafin yanzu yana ɗauke da isassun bangarori masu goyan baya don jin kamar tebur ɗin canja wuri na gaske maimakon ƙirar gwarzo ɗaya mai iyo.",
      "The page now feels like a real part of the football product instead of two floating cards in a dark void.": "Shafin yanzu yana jin kamar ainihin ɓangaren samfurin ƙwallon ƙafa maimakon katunan iyo biyu a cikin duhu.",
      "The page now uses football-native room types, not generic social placeholders.": "Shafin a yanzu yana amfani da nau'ikan dakin wasan ƙwallon ƙafa, ba masu zaman jama'a ba.",
      "The Palmeiras holding midfielder keeps showing first-contact calm under pressure. His interceptions are impressive, but the bigger point is how often he stabilizes the next pass.": "Dan wasan tsakiya na Palmeiras yana ci gaba da nuna kwanciyar hankali na tuntuɓar matsi. Tsangwamarsa yana da ban sha'awa, amma babban batu shine sau nawa ya tabbatar da wucewa na gaba.",
      "The point is to show structure, intent, and future football logic without pretending the backend systems already exist.": "Ma'anar ita ce nuna tsari, niyya, da dabarun ƙwallon ƙafa na gaba ba tare da yin riya cewa tsarin baya ya wanzu ba.",
      "The right rail should add football meaning, not just stack more text cards": "Madaidaicin dogo ya kamata ya ƙara ma'anar ƙwallon ƙafa, ba kawai tara ƙarin katunan rubutu ba",
      "The same product logic applies here: big women’s fixtures belong in the same room ecology.": "Dabarar samfurin iri ɗaya ya shafi a nan: manyan kayan aikin mata suna cikin yanayin ɗaki ɗaya.",
      "Their last four matches show a sharper overlap-to-cutback pattern and better counterpress recovery.": "Matsalolin su huɗu na ƙarshe sun nuna tsarin daidaitawa-zuwa yankan baya da mafi kyawun dawo da latsawa.",
      "Their last three defensive structures collapse passing lanes faster, which is changing the Bellingham load in possession.": "Tsarin tsaro uku na ƙarshe ya rushe hanyoyin wucewa cikin sauri, wanda ke canza nauyin Bellingham a mallaka.",
      "Their latest run of matches keeps reinforcing the same wide-to-box pattern, and it belongs in the main feed, not a separate lane.": "Sabbin wasanninsu na matches suna ci gaba da ƙarfafa tsarin faxi-zuwa-akwatin, kuma yana cikin babban abinci, ba wata hanya dabam ba.",
      "Their right-half-space creation keeps widening the shot map.": "Ƙirƙirar rabin rabin sarari na dama yana ci gaba da faɗaɗa taswirar harbi.",
      "Themes": "Jigogi",
      "These preview pages now sit inside the same football product language as Market XI, instead of looking like giant heroes with nothing underneath.": "Waɗannan shafukan samfoti yanzu suna zaune a cikin yaren samfurin ƙwallon ƙafa iri ɗaya kamar Market XI, maimakon kamannin manyan jarumai waɗanda ba komai a ƙasa.",
      "These rooms are structured demo surfaces only. No live moderation, messaging, or presence engine is being claimed here yet.": "Waɗannan dakunan an tsara su ne kawai filayen demo. Babu daidaitawa kai tsaye, saƙo, ko injin kasancewar da ake da'awar a nan tukuna.",
      "They are sustaining width without exposing the first counter line, which keeps their risers stable.": "Suna ɗorewa nisa ba tare da fallasa layin farko ba, wanda ke sa masu hawan su tsayayyu.",
      "This community surface is a structured demo only, not a live messaging stack.": "Wannan saman al'umma tsarin demo ne kawai, ba tarin saƙon kai tsaye ba.",
      "This page is denser and stronger, but still clearly marked as a concept surface.": "Wannan shafin ya fi girma kuma ya fi ƙarfi, amma har yanzu ana yi masa alama a fili azaman saman ra'ayi.",
      "This page is intentionally fuller than a placeholder, but it still does not claim live game systems, real persistence, or backend-backed competition logic.": "Wannan shafin ya cika da gangan fiye da mai sanya wuri, amma har yanzu baya da'awar tsarin wasan kai tsaye, dagewa na gaske, ko dabarun gasa mai goyon baya.",
      "Three clubs still project inside one title window.": "Kungiyoyi uku har yanzu suna aiki a cikin taga taken guda ɗaya.",
      "Three women’s names in active watch": "Sunayen mata guda uku a cikin agogon aiki",
      "Title races tracked": "An bi diddigin tseren taken",
      "Title-pressure watch in the same slate.": "Agogon take-matsi a cikin slate iri ɗaya.",
      "Today’s slate": "Slate na yau",
